snippet.title: Amber Nykole
snippet.description:
Hello! and welcome :) I'm Amber Nykole-- an entrepreneur, unschool mom of 3, voice over actress, teacher, and vegetarian---- amongst many other labels you may want to slap on me. Really I'm a spiritual soul having a human experience...  I hope my videos help and inspire you to transform your life so that you become the best version of yourself! 

I am a visionary creative and have overcame drug abuse, alcohol abuse, rescued my new family from homelessness, and awakened to my true potential-- all without a college degree.  I dream, envision, and then create possibility in my life --and I will show you how to--too! 

i think differently.  and I reject the status-quo. i question societal mainframes often and draw conclusions based on my heart truth. i hope you will too... I am here to guide you , inspire you, and transform your ego back to source-- Truth.  

I look forward to sharing this journey along with you, my soul friends. As we meet again--once again --in this life and many before.
